title: Conquering 'I'm Not Good Enough'
itunes:title: Conquering 'I'm Not Good Enough'
description:
We all question whether or not we are good enough; that is called the impostor syndrome. In this episode, we are going to talk about how to conquer the impostor syndrome so that you can stop holding yourself back from what it truly is that you want to do.
